text = "[b]Music by Kevin MacLeod[/b] ([color=blue][url=https://incompetech.com]incompetech.com[/url][/color])
Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 4.0 License
[color=blue][url=http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/]http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/[/url][/color]

Featured Tracks:
 - Carefree
 - Fluffing a Duck
 - Investigations
 - Local Forecast - Elevator
 - Merry Go - Distressed
 - Monkeys Spinning Monkeys
 - Scheming Weasel (Faster)
 - Sneaky Snitch
 - The Builder
 - Wallpaper
 - Winner Winner

Note on Audio:
Original tracks have been converted to .OGG format for technical optimization. Additionally, real-time processing (pitch-shifting, speed manipulation) is applied dynamically to reflect the environment.

[b]SFX[/b]
From pixabay"
